Package com.charliai.activities.api

Class Entities

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.charliai.activities.api.Entities
  • public class Entities
extends java.lang.Object
    The Entities class supports all the processing and in-memory storage of multiple entity objects during activity processing. Each intent sent in an activity request can contain zero to many entities. This class consolidates all the entities and stores entity objects for processing.
    Author:
    kevincollins

      • Entities

        public Entities​(org.json.JSONArray entities)
        The Entities instantiation method will create a new entities object based on the JSON Array passed as a parameter. The formatted JSON must match in the standard JSON required by the entities message format.
        Parameters:
        entities - JSONArray of entities
